    dc:description "FIGURES 5–7. Color pattern of Baetis majus Tiunova sp. nov., larvae, paratypes: 5, male, dorsal view; 6, ventral view; 7, female, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736178/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736180>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–13. Baetis majus Tiunova sp. nov., larvae, dorsal view, paratypes: 8, scape; 9, surface of the head; 10, spatulas on head; 11, canines of left and right mandible; 12, glossae and paraglossae; 13, setae on paraglossa. Scale bar: 8, 11–12, 0.01 mm; 9, 0.02 mm; 10, 13, 0.002 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736180/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736182>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14–20. Baetis majus Tiunova sp. nov., larvae, details of mouthparts, paratypes: 14, labrum, dorsal view; 15, canines and prostheca of right mandible, dorsal view; 16, canines and prostheca of left mandible, dorsal view; 17, maxillary palp, dorsal view; 18, glossa and paraglossa, ventral view; 19, labial palp, ventral view; 20, labial palp, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736182/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736186>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21–26. Baetis majus Tiunova sp. nov., larvae, paratypes, dorsal view: 21, foreleg, 22, shape of long bristles on distal part of femora; 23, shape of short setae on inner margin femora; 24, tarsus claw; 25, paraproct plate; 26, posterior margin of tergum VI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736186/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736188>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27–32. Baetis majus Tiunova sp. nov., larvae, paratypes: 27, 29, inner margin of fore tibia; 28, inner margin of fore tarsus; 30, tarsal claw; 31, paraproct; 32, spatulas on paraproct. Scale bar: 27–31, 0.01 mm; 32, 0.001 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736188/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736190>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33–38. Baetis majus Tiunova sp. nov., larvae, gills shape, dorsal view, roman numbers belong to the respective gill pairs." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736190/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736192>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39–41. Baetis majus Tiunova sp. nov., egg: 39, general view; 40, structure of chorion; 41, micropyle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736192/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736194>
    dc:description "FIGURE 42. Locality of Baetis majus Tiunova sp. nov., Shkotovka River (Primorskiy Kray)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736194/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736196>
    dc:description "FIGURE 43. Bayesian tree based on mitochondrion COI gene for subgenera Baetis and Tenuibaetis form Eastern and Western Palearctic, Nearctic and Oriental regions. Specimens obtained in this study are in bold. Bayesian posterior probabilities (PP) above 0.7 are given above tree nodes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736196/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736198>
    dc:description "FIGURE 44. Bayesian tree of the genus Baetis inferred from the cytochrome c oxidase I (COI) nucleotide sequence data (466 bp) and 47 morphological characters. Two species of Labiobaetis were used as outgroup. All data including species-groups are taken from Sroka (2012). Specimen obtained in this study is in bold. Bayesian posterior probabilities (PP) above 0.7 are given above tree nodes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4736198/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

